  m_Name: Song_of_the_Steed
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::AbilitySO
  abilityName: Song of the Steed
  description: "Speak in a voice comprehensible to horses.\nThey need reasoning with,
    but are inclined to\ntrust you.\nPASSION - Certainty\nRestore SPI when you prove
    somebody wrong.\nA perfect steed is neither wild nor tamed\nAs one, a streak
    aguele through green untamed\nSaddle Knight\nLOYAL STEED\nAppearance Temperament\n1
    Pristine Completely silent\n2 Plaited Highly alert\n3 Tall Eternally valiant\n4
    Golden Fierce (d8 trample)\n5 Dark Loved by other beasts\n6 Stocky Perfect sense
    of\ndirection\nKNIGHTED BY...\nThe Jewelled Seer\nVIG 6, CLA 6, SPI 16, 1 GD\n\u2022
    No body is visible, just layers and layers\nof jewelled silk and glittering lace.\n\u2022
    Can see the history of jewelled items, and\nthe locations of their own jewels.\n\u2022
    Wants to send their jewels out to remote\nplaces, watching from afar.\nPerson:
    Stocky hunter ~ Name: Knotte ~ Characteristic: Lice infested\nObject: Silver
    armour ~ Beast: Draft horse ~ State: Dying ~ Theme: Food\n1\n9\nThe"
